   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Because more than one user may have access to agreement documents on an agreement record,
         you may come across a situation where another user has checked out the document. </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">From the Lock Status tab, you can click the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Refresh Lock</uicontrol> button at
         any time to display the current lock status for the open document (except for when you have
         checked out the document already). If the document is checked out by another user, the only
         actions you can take are to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">List Agreements</b> and Refresh Lock. </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Consider the following example:</p>
      <note type="note" id="note_afc_rkn_12c" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Use Case: Reacquiring the document lock from another user</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">You have opened a contract document version from the agreement's Document Version
            Details in Microsoft Word. Another user checks out the document before you.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">A message is displayed showing that the other user controls the lock.</p>
         <fig id="fig_hd5_hpj_12c" class="- topic/fig ">
            <image height="400"
                   placement="break"
                   href="../attachments/45220101/49676312.png"
                   id="image_id5_hpj_12c"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The document cannot be checked out, because another user has already locked it. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">You click on the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Lock Status</uicontrol> tab to view the current lock status.
            The "Document locked by" field shows the document is locked by another user.</p>
         <fig id="fig_pmh_lpj_12c" class="- topic/fig ">
            <image height="400"
                   placement="break"
                   href="../attachments/45220101/49676313.png"
                   id="image_qmh_lpj_12c"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The other user releases the document lock or checks in a new version. You click
               <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Refresh Lock</uicontrol> to refresh the current lock status. The pane
            refreshes, showing updated lock status details.</p>
         <fig id="fig_vn4_npj_12c" class="- topic/fig ">
            <image height="400"
                   placement="break"
                   href="../attachments/45220101/49676311.png"
                   id="image_wn4_npj_12c"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
         <p class="- topic/p ">You click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Acquire Lock</uicontrol> to lock the document and start working.
            All menu items are enabled.</p>
      </note>
